title: Desirable Location! Privacy and 1 Acre 611 Fernwood,
text:
Desirable Location! Privacy and 1 Acre 611 Fernwood, ad date: 10/17/2015 
Privacy and 1 Acre 611 Fernwood, Crescent City, CA. Very nice home on a secluded street, located off of Parkway Drive. 3 bedrooms, 2 baths on 1 acre. Home has a wonderful feel. It's as if you are in the woods right after leaving town. Wonderful location! Short drive to town. Total interior remodel of home. All new stainless steel appliances, monitor heater, new flooring, new paint, new kitchen cabinets, new everything!!! The list goes on! This home is a definite must see! Priced right! MLS 1500463 $235,000
